data.description: 265 Ridge Mill Drive - Welcome home to this charming end unit townhome in the highly sought after Ridge Mill community. This home features 3 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The open concept kitchen flows to the family room, creating a welcoming space for everyday living. Recent updates include flooring, paint, and HVAC, all completed within the last 5 years. The HOA includes maintenance of the grounds, exterior, termite, and trash. HOA also handles the roof, which was just inspected. The community offers a large pool and playground and is conveniently located to restaurants and shopping. Don't miss this opportunity!
